<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>FontSwap — Ami Steelman</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@300;400;500&family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --slate-deep: #1C2B3A;
      --slate-mid: #3D5A6B;
      --steel: #5B8FA8;
      --fog: #A8BCC8;
      --ice: #E8EEF2;
      --ink: #1C2B3A;
      --ink-secondary: #3D5A6B;
      --ink-tertiary: #7A96A6;
      --surface: #F4F7F9;
      --rule: #D6E2E9;
      --white: #ffffff;
    }

    html { font-size: 16px; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 300;
      background: var(--surface);
      color: var(--ink);
      line-height: 1.8;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    header {
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
      padding: 1.5rem 0;
      background: var(--white);
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 680px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 2rem;
    }

    .site-name {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--ink);
      text-decoration: none;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    .site-name span {
      color: var(--steel);
      font-weight: 300;
    }

    .hero {
      background: var(--slate-deep);
      padding: 4rem 0;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .hero-logo {
      font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 3rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -1px;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .hero-logo .f { color: var(--ice); }
    .hero-logo .s { color: var(--steel); }

    .hero-tagline {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--fog);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.75rem;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: background 0.15s;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--steel);
      color: var(--white);
    }

    .btn-primary:hover { background: #4a7a91; }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--fog);
      border: 1px solid var(--slate-mid);
      margin-left: 0.75rem;
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover { color: var(--ice); }

    main {
      padding: 4rem 0 6rem;
    }

    .page-label {
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--steel);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    h1 {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.25rem);
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1.2;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      color: var(--ink);
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .intro {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--ink-secondary);
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      border-left: 2px solid var(--steel);
      background: rgba(91, 143, 168, 0.06);
      border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;
    }

    section { margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }

    h2 {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--ink);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      padding-top: 2.5rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    }

    section:first-of-type h2 {
      border-top: none;
      padding-top: 0;
    }

    p {
      color: var(--ink-secondary);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 300;
    }

    p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

    ul {
      list-style: none;
      margin: 0.75rem 0 1rem;
    }

    ul li {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--ink-secondary);
      padding: 0.4rem 0 0.4rem 1.25rem;
      position: relative;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    }

    ul li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

    ul li::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      width: 4px;
      height: 4px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--steel);
      opacity: 0.6;
    }

    .step {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      align-items: flex-start;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .step-num {
      font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--white);
      background: var(--steel);
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-top: 0.15rem;
    }

    .step p { margin-bottom: 0; }

    .privacy-note {
      margin-top: 3rem;
      padding: 2rem;
      border: 1px solid var(--rule);
      border-radius: 8px;
      background: var(--white);
    }

    .privacy-note p { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }

    .privacy-note a {
      color: var(--steel);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
      padding: 2rem 0;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
      color: var(--ink-tertiary);
      background: var(--white);
    }

    footer .container {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    footer a {
      color: var(--ink-tertiary);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    footer a:hover { color: var(--ink); }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .container { padding: 0 1.25rem; }
      main { padding: 2.5rem 0 4rem; }
      .hero { padding: 2.5rem 0; }
      .hero-logo { font-size: 2rem; }
      footer .container { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <div class="container">
      <a href="/" class="site-name">ami<span>steelman</span></a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-logo">
      <span class="f">F</span><span class="s">S</span>
    </div>
    <p class="hero-tagline">Swap fonts across Google Slides™ and Docs™ in one click.</p>
    <a href="https://workspace.google.com/marketplace" class="btn btn-primary">Install from Marketplace</a>
    <a href="/privacy" class="btn btn-secondary">Privacy Policy</a>
  </div>

  <main>
    <div class="container">

      <p class="page-label">// tools</p>
      <h1>FontSwap</h1>

      <p class="intro">
        FontSwap is a free Google Workspace™ add-on that scans your entire document for fonts and replaces them in seconds — including tables, speaker notes, headers, and footers.
      </p>

      <section>
        <h2>What it does</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Scans your entire Google Slides™ or Google Docs™ file for all fonts in use</li>
          <li>Replaces any font with any Google Fonts family in one click</li>
          <li>Covers tables, speaker notes, masters, layouts, headers, and footers</li>
          <li>10–50× faster than manual font replacement</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>How to use it</h2>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">1</div>
          <p>Install FontSwap from the Google Workspace™ Marketplace.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">2</div>
          <p>Open any Google Slides™ presentation or Google Docs™ document.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">3</div>
          <p>Go to <strong>Extensions → FontSwap → Start FontSwap</strong>.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">4</div>
          <p>Choose the font to replace, enter a Google Fonts family name, and click Replace.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Works with</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Google Slides™</li>
          <li>Google Docs™</li>
          <li>Any Google Fonts family</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <div class="privacy-note">
        <p style="font-weight: 500; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Your data stays yours.</p>
        <p>FontSwap only reads font metadata within your open document and never stores, logs, or transmits any of your content. All processing happens within Google's infrastructure.</p>
        <p style="margin-top: 0.75rem;"><a href="/privacy">Read the full privacy policy →</a></p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <div class="container">
      <span>© 2026 Ami Steelman</span>
      <a href="/">amisteelman.com</a>
    </div>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
